'''拉马拉和比雷赫省'''（{{lang-ar|محافظة رام الله والبيرة}}；''{{transl|ar|DIN|Muḥāfaẓat Rām Allāh wa l Bīra}}''），又譯'''拉姆安拉和比雷省'''<ref name="zhihu">{{zhihu |id=112331816 |type=zhuanlan |url=https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/112331816 |title=巴勒斯坦姑娘莉娜·苏蕾比——国际劳动妇女节特辑 |access-date=2022-03-07}}</ref>，為[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]16個[[巴勒斯坦行政区划|行政區劃]]之一。這個省涵蓋[[約旦河西岸地區|西岸地區]]中部一大片，位處[[耶路撒冷省|耶路撒冷省]]的北方邊界，為西岸地區中部最大面積的行政區，首府為{{tsl|en|al-Bireh|比雷赫}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.al-bireh.org/english/al-bireh_city.htm |title= :: Al-Bireh Municipality ::<!-- Bot generated title --> |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080620012123/http://www.al-bireh.org/english/al-bireh_city.htm |archive-date=2008-06-20 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pnic.gov.ps/english/geography/Residential_%20gatherings.html |title=Administrative divisions in Palestine |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061223052603/http://www.pnic.gov.ps/english/geography/Residential_%20gatherings.html |archive-date=2006-12-23 |language=en}}</ref>。

根據{{tsl|en|Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics|巴勒斯坦中央統計局}}（{{lang|en|Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics}}；PCBS）統計，拉马拉和比雷赫省於2007年人口為279,730人<ref name="pcbs">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcbs.gov.ps/Portals/_pcbs/census2007/ind_loca_09.pdf |publisher=Palestinian National Authority, Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics |title=Population, Housing and Establishment Census 2007  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101114002607/http://www.pcbs.gov.ps/Portals/_pcbs/census2007/ind_loca_09.pdf |archive-date=2010-11-14 |format=PDF |access-date=2010-12-03 |language=ar-ps,en}}</ref>。現時的省長是[[莱伊拉·甘纳姆|莱伊拉·甘纳姆]]博士（Laylā Ghannām），她亦是巴勒斯坦的首位女省長{{r|zhihu}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.elanthemag.com/index.php/site/blog_detail/ramallah_appoints_first_female_governor_just_dont_mess_with_her-nid85864597/ |title=Archived copy |access-date=2011-04-02 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101216055145/http://www.elanthemag.com/index.php/site/blog_detail/ramallah_appoints_first_female_governor_just_dont_mess_with_her-nid85864597/ |archive-date=2010-12-16 |language=en}}</ref>。

